# YouTrack MCP Project Overview

This project implements a Model Context Protocol (MCP) server for interacting with YouTrack instances. It provides tools for managing YouTrack agile boards, sprints, issues, and projects through a standardized MCP interface.

## Key Components

- **Main Entry Point**: [index.ts](mdc:src/index.ts) - Application entry point
- **MCP Server**: [server.ts](mdc:src/server.ts) - Sets up the MCP server
- **YouTrack Client**: [youtrack-client.ts](mdc:src/youtrack-client.ts) - API client for YouTrack

## Available Tools

The MCP server provides these tools for YouTrack interaction:

- `youtrack_list_boards` - List all available agile boards
- `youtrack_get_board` - Get details of a specific board
- `youtrack_get_sprint` - Get details of a specific sprint
- `youtrack_find_sprints` - Find sprints by board, name, status, or time period
- `youtrack_get_issue` - Get details of a specific issue
- `youtrack_update_issue` - Update an existing issue
- `youtrack_search_issues` - Search for issues using YouTrack query syntax
- `youtrack_find_issues_by_criteria` - Find issues by criteria
- `youtrack_list_projects` - List all available projects
- `youtrack_find_projects_by_name` - Find projects by name

